der: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-49\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-50\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">100</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-51\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">)</span>&nbsp;бүхэл тоог оруулна. Энэ нь нийт өрөөний тоо.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Дараагийн&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span>&nbsp;мөрүүдийн&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">i</span>-р мөр нь&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Element-10-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; line-height: normal; word-spacing: normal; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: black !important;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-58\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 1.193em;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 0.955em; height: 0px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: 0px; word-spacing: normal;\">p</span><span style=\"word-spacing: normal;\"><sub>i</sub></span></span></span></span>,&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Element-